name: 주인공
dialog: I was waiting for Himchan today to exercise together.

name: Himchan
dialog: Oh, you finally fell in love with the charm of exercise. Hahaha.

name: Himchan
dialog: Last time we did some stretching to warm up, remember?

name: 주인공
dialog: Oh, I remember. I felt lighter after the stretching.

name: Himchan
dialog: Today we're going to do some stretching again, let's try different movements. Let's go!

name: Himchan
dialog: Remember, when exercising, make sure to do it with your parents, get certified, and be safe.

name: Himchan
dialog: First, sit cross-legged and imagine someone lifting you up from above your head, and your back will straighten. Then, keep the distance between your shoulders and ears as far as possible, and pull your chin towards your body.

name: Himchan
dialog: Next, try the next movement. Let's go!

name: Himchan
dialog: That's because you're getting friendly with exercising.

name: Himchan
